item.title: Study Migration Tool
item.description: Study Migration Tool has been added to Open SCE. Study Migration Tool is a Plotly-Dash Python application developed by Achieve Intelligence that generates visualisations of study milestone activity for analysis and migration scheduling. The full code of this package is available in Open SCE (GitHub)
